# ─── Linux CommandCrafter — environment variables ───────────────────────────
#
# Copy this file to `.env` and fill in your values.
# NEVER commit your real `.env` to version control.
#
# ⚠  Security note: Variables prefixed with VITE_ are embedded in the
#    client-side JavaScript bundle at build time and are therefore visible
#    to anyone who inspects the page source or network traffic.
#    Do NOT put secrets here that must stay private — treat this key as a
#    public API key that is rate-limited / scoped to your domain.
#
#    For higher-security deployments, move the Gemini call to a backend
#    proxy (e.g. a Cloudflare Worker or Express server) and keep the key
#    server-side only.
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

# Google Gemini API key — required for the Command Analyzer feature.
# Get yours at https://aistudio.google.com/app/apikey
VITE_GEMINI_API_KEY=
